    "description": {
      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You have mastered techniques to take advantage of every drop in any enemy's guard, gaining the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">When you hit a creature with an opportunity attack, the creature's speed becomes 0 for the rest of the turn.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Creatures provoke opportunity attacks from you even if they take the @action[Disengage] action before leaving your reach.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When a creature within 5 feet of you makes an attack against a target other than you (and that target doesn't have this feat), you can use your reaction to make a melee weapon attack against the attacking creature.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
